Brian and Joan Ogden, from Wigan, had been out to eat in Benidorm .
They were on their way back to their hotel in Ben Pancho when they were robbed .
A thief reached into Mr Ogden's pocket while his accomplice stood between them .
The pair followed the crooks out of the hotel and asked for the wallet .
Mr Ogden got the wallet back and got it back to Mrs Ogden .